lead_paragraph: Lucas Pouille clinched his first career title on Sunday, beating top-seeded Dominic Thiem of Austria 7-6 (5), 6-2 to win the Moselle Open final.

headline.print_headline: Pouille Beats Thiem to Win Moselle Open and 1st Title
headline.main: Pouille Beats Thiem to Win Moselle Open and 1st Title
